room_title: Escape room "The Voyage of the Nautilus" by Cloak and Dagger Escape Rooms in Princeton
review: I had my daughter's 14th birthday party here today in "The Voyage of the Nautilus" room. Everyone had such a great time, kids and adults. Great experience and would recommend it to anyone. We can't wait to come back in June for my son's birthday party and try "The Search for the Jade Skull" room!

room_title: Escape room "The Voyage of the Nautilus" by Cloak and Dagger Escape Rooms in Princeton
review: Awesome rooms! Did the Skull room last week, and today completed the Nautilus room. So well put together, and just difficult enough. Hopefully, they are planning on opening another location!
